== Ebuild repository ==

The [[Project:Emacs|Emacs project]] runs an [[ebuild repository]] for GNU Emacs and XEmacs (see [[Project:Emacs/Overlay]]) which contains a number of packages including many VCS builds. To add the repository:

{{RootCmd|eselect repository enable emacs|emerge --sync emacs}}
or
{{RootCmd|layman -a emacs}}

Many more emacs-related packages should now be available for installation.

